{"pages":[{},{}],"posts":[{"title":"每个人都是孤独的","date":"2020-10-08T06:43:54.000Z","path":"2020/10/08/每个人都是孤独的/","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>皎洁的月光</p>\n<p>请洁净我</p>\n<p>洗净年月泼的墨</p>\n<p>熄灭我吞下的烟火</p>\n<p>​                                        —《孤独》邓紫棋</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>很长的一段时间，直到现在，我一直觉得我只有可能是孤身一人。得到的终会失去，拥有的终会消失。这个世界上没有什么东西能够让我守候。我惶恐过，我绝望过，甚至手足无措，不知道究竟该怎么办。那段时间真的是过的很绝望呀。其实，随着时间的推移，我好像也习惯了吧，孤独是人的本质，我是不可能想办法摆脱它的。</p>\n<p>这两天好烦呀，我感觉我的世界有点冷冰冰的。我和爸爸之间没有一点共同语言，不管干啥还是在哪里，爸爸嘴里只有学习。以前是高考，现在是考研，不管是为了找话题还是啥，反正就是老说。我承认我的想法不够理性，可我现在就是想放纵自己讨厌爸爸，我实在有点受不了这样过着。我是知道爸爸小时候的经历，知道他受的苦受的累。没有接受过好的教育自然是想让下一代好好学习，可我现在觉得爸爸除了学习之外没有教给我其他任何东西。</p>\n<p>有人可能会说我就是傻，怎么啥都不干还指望着让爸爸教我啥，觉得我头不合适，没错我就是头不合适。我从来都没有觉得家里的氛围让我感觉非常的好。总是欠点什么。10月2号是我20岁的生日，家里总共有8个人（有个婴儿），怎么说，我宁愿自己一个人过生日也不想有人陪我过生日。国庆这7天天天呆在家里打游戏，我会觉得自己很可恶吗？没有吧，家里的氛围怎么能让我好好学，我就是理由多怎么了？我就是想堕落了有人能管得了我吗？</p>\n<p>我从来都没想过未来我要干什么。有那么一段时间我是真的觉得未来是虚无缥缈的，幻想未来还不如好好的活在当下（虽然我能感觉我的想法有不小问题）。我现在满脑子都是一两年后考研的事，可我现在又不太想考研。不如去看一场解解的演唱会？好像也没什么欲望，奇怪的很。</p>\n<p>解解出了新歌《孤独》，这首歌的词写的挺好的，有意境有深度。曲子有月光的影子，鼓点也很突出。我似乎还没有get到点上，再听一听应该就上头了。应该会有很多人听完都会感同身受吧。其实我们都一样，都会有孤独的时候。每个人都是孤独的，而当你夜不能寐时能够想到有很多人也像你一样睡不着，你应该不会感觉有那么孤单了吧。</p>\n","excerpt":"","tags":[]},{"title":"第8章 IO库","date":"2020-10-01T08:51:28.000Z","path":"2020/10/01/第8章-IO库/","content":"<h1 id=\"8-1-IO类\"><a href=\"#8-1-IO类\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"8.1 IO类\"></a>8.1 IO类</h1><p>IO库类型和头文件</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>头文件</th>\n<th>类型</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>iostream</td>\n<td>istream，wistream从流读取数据<br>ostream，wostream向流写入数据<br>iostream，wiostream读写流</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>fstream</td>\n<td>ifstream，wifstream从文件读取数据<br>ofstream，wofstream向文件写入数据<br>fstream，wfstream读写文件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>sstream</td>\n<td>istringstream，wistringstream从string读取数据<br>ostringstream，wostringstream向string写入数据<br>stringstream，wstringstream读写string</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"1，IO对象无拷贝或赋值\"><a href=\"#1，IO对象无拷贝或赋值\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1，IO对象无拷贝或赋值\"></a>1，IO对象无拷贝或赋值</h2><figure class=\"highlight c++\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ofstream out1, out2;</span><br><span class=\"line\">out1 = out2;\t\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">// 错误：：不能对流对象赋值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\">ofstream <span class=\"title\">print</span><span class=\"params\">(ofstream)</span></span>;\t<span class=\"comment\">// 错误：不能初始化ofstream参数</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">out2 = print(out2)\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">// 错误：不能拷贝流对象</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>由于不能拷贝IO对象，因此我们也==不能将形参或返回类型设置为流类型==。</p>\n<p>进行IO操作的函数==通常以引用方式传递和返回流==。且传递和返回的引用不能是const的。</p>\n<h2 id=\"2，条件状态\"><a href=\"#2，条件状态\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2，条件状态\"></a>2，条件状态</h2><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>strm::iostate</th>\n<th>（strm是一种IO类型）iostate是一种机器相关的类型，提供了表达条件状态的完整功能</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>strm::badbit</td>\n<td>用来指出流已崩溃</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>strm::failbit</td>\n<td>用来指出一个IO操作失败了</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>strm::eofbit</td>\n<td>用来指出流到达了文件结束</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>strm::goodbit</td>\n<td>用来指出流未处于错误状态。此值保证为零</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>s.eof()</td>\n<td>若流s的eofbit置位</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n","excerpt":"","tags":[{"name":"C++","slug":"C","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/C/"}]},{"title":"第7章 类","date":"2020-09-27T10:59:47.000Z","path":"2020/09/27/第7章-类/","content":"","excerpt":"","tags":[]},{"title":"Test","date":"2020-09-21T03:33:17.000Z","path":"2020/09/21/Test/","content":"<h1 id=\"ddd\"><a href=\"#ddd\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ddd\"></a>ddd</h1><p>defgfgnbmafdsmviamfvavfavav</p>\n","excerpt":"","tags":[{"name":"C++","slug":"C","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/C/"},{"name":"C","slug":"C","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/C/"},{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/Python/"}]},{"title":"Hello World","date":"2020-09-20T13:31:44.373Z","path":"2020/09/20/hello-world/","content":"<p>Welcome to <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvLw==\">Hexo<i class=\"fa fa-external-link-alt\"></i></span>! This is your very first post. Check <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mv\">documentation<i class=\"fa fa-external-link-alt\"></i></span> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3MvdHJvdWJsZXNob290aW5nLmh0bWw=\">troubleshooting<i class=\"fa fa-external-link-alt\"></i></span> or you can ask me on <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2hleG9qcy9oZXhvL2lzc3Vlcw==\">GitHub<i class=\"fa fa-external-link-alt\"></i></span>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mvd3JpdGluZy5odG1s\">Writing<i class=\"fa fa-external-link-alt\"></i></span></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mvc2VydmVyLmh0bWw=\">Server<i class=\"fa fa-external-link-alt\"></i></span></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3MvZ2VuZXJhdGluZy5odG1s\">Generating<i class=\"fa fa-external-link-alt\"></i></span></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mvb25lLWNvbW1hbmQtZGVwbG95bWVudC5odG1s\">Deployment<i class=\"fa fa-external-link-alt\"></i></span></p>\n","excerpt":"","tags":[]}],"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"C++","slug":"C","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/C/"},{"name":"C","slug":"C","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/C/"},{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","permalink":"http://example.com/tags/Python/"}]}